Egill Thordarson from the advertising agency Peel, who created the ads in collaboration with the international advertising agency M&C Saatchi, says the reception has been better than expected.
"I have been to many Inspired By Iceland tours that have gone very well, but this new tour is already surpassing them.
At its core, this is about creating PR value, that is, getting foreign media to talk about the expedition, and it has gone incredibly well.
