Therefore, the concerned person has not received an automatic invitation to take the test.
Camilla says many have followed the homecoming exemption rules even though they filled out the registration form in English and in some cases employers have also been vigilant in sending people for testing again after they arrived in the country.
"This will be looked into this week on how to make it easier for people to access this to draw attention to the process."
